bowling balls and a rubber band.
Do you understand?

32:04.000 --> 32:06.920
&lt; Yes, sir!

32:06.920 --> 32:10.920
There. Capital T stands for Tommy,
top and Toto, too.

32:11.840 --> 32:15.240
   Now, you take a crack at it.

32:15.240 --> 32:19.040
I know you can do it.
You know you can do it.

32:19.040 --> 32:20.680
   One block on top of another,

32:20.680 --> 32:24.400
and before you know it
you've built a castle.

32:24.400 --> 32:25.440
Hi.

