 Wasn't expecting you till later.

32:27.600 --> 32:31.000
The board of trustees stalled
my community outreach proposals.

32:31.000 --> 32:32.920
       You want a drink?  No.

32:32.920 --> 32:36.920
THUNDER

32:42.800 --> 32:45.440
17 years of drought -

32:45.440 --> 32:49.440
Profits, profits, profits.
Boston, Detroit.

32:50.320 --> 32:53.920
All those poor,
diseased, dying people.

32:53.920 --> 32:57.920
The only differences
are  the resources and the apathy
   of those who control them.

32:58.960 --> 33:00.720
You know how selfish we are?

33:00.720 --> 33:04.720
We're a nation of card-carrying
neurotics more interested in tax
            loopholes

33:05.360 --> 33:08.080
than we are with
helping our fellow man.

33:08.080 --> 33:12.080
I've seen Ethiopians die with more
dignity than some Americans live.

33:12.680 --> 33:15.240
And I promised myself I was
gonna try to change that.

33:15.240 --> 33:18.640
Donald, you come down off the
mountain sounding like Moses

33:18.640 --> 33:21.080
and expect the whole world to
fall in step behind you.

33:21.080 --> 33:25.080
It doesn't work that way. You did
the same thing when Marine died.

33:25.360 --> 33:28.280
Oh, please, Constance. I just
went 15 rounds at the hospital.

33:28.280 --> 33:29.880
        That damn hospital!

33:29.880 --> 33:32.960
You and I were doing the vigil,
Tommy was a baby,

33:32.960 --> 33:36.960
Lizzy barely knew what was happening
except that her mother
was on those horrible machines.

33:38.000 --> 33:42.000
The kids and I went around the corner
for ice-cream, we came back
and it was over.

33:42.760 --> 33:45.600
You'd told them to pull the
plug on my sister's life.

33:45.600 --> 33:47.920
I did what I thought was right.

33:47.920 --> 33:51.920
And expected me to forgive you.
You wouldn't share the burden
of that decision with anyone,

33:52.240 --> 33:54.360
  because you had to be a martyr.

33:54.360 --> 33:57.160
You won't let anyone help
you bring up the kids,

33:57.160 --> 33:58.400
you wanna do that by yourself, too.

33:58.400 --> 34:02.400
Now you're getting kicked around
because you want to solve
the world's problems.

34:03.040 --> 34:07.040
What's in it for you,
Donald, besides punishment?

34:17.520 --> 34:20.040
                Oh!

34:20.040 --> 34:24.040
      I knew you could do it!

34:29.000 --> 34:30.719
       Tell you what, Rudi,

34:30.719 --> 34:34.199
I'll give you a chance
to win back some of your money.

34:34.199 --> 34:38.199
How are you, Keith?

34:40.360 --> 34:41.920
Now, say you're sorry.

34:41.920 --> 34:43.679
Now, say you're sorry.
I'm sorry.

34:43.679 --> 34:47.120
That was very good, Keith.

34:47.120 --> 34:51.120
Now, bark like a dog.

